{"tid":178214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Brexit 正式啟動！！！","createTime":"2017-03-29T11:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:24:17.000Z","uid":29081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8a8e43e2254d731e65e75ebec51e07d9b188cf","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"BBC Breaking News<br />\nThe EU has received the letter from UK that will trigger Article 50 &amp; formally begin the #Brexit process<br />\n<br />\nbbc.in/2nzKvC9 #BrexitDay"},{"pid":"58fd2a32e044c45d687ee051b346c8ca431c1501","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"UK formally begins two year process of leaving EU with letter triggering Article 50 of the Lisbon treaty<br />\n<br />\nbbc.in/2nLlrsf #BrexitDay"},{"pid":"7b070c4abd9a6e9d978f6b7a8b244af21f0e47e9","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"【歷史時刻】英國向歐盟遞「分手信」 正式啟動脫歐<br />\n<br />\n英國今日正式向歐盟發信表達脫歐意願，首相文翠珊按《里斯本條約》第50條啟動脫歐程序，英國駐歐盟大使巴羅（Tim Barrow）親手將信交予歐洲理事會主席圖斯克（Donald Tusk）。<br />\n<br />\n英國啟動脫歐後，在接下來的48小時，圖斯克會向其餘27個歐盟成員國遞交談判指引草案，英國與歐盟將展開為期兩年談判。歐盟領袖將於4月29日召開特別高峯會，通過英國脫歐談判方針，估計要到5月中旬至月底才會真正與倫敦展開談判。<br />\n<br />\n英國脫歐期間，國內政治難免有暗湧，蘇格蘭及北愛爾蘭在去年公投中支持留歐，蘇格蘭首席部長施雅晴有意推動第二次蘇獨公投，而目前北愛爾蘭因兩大黨籌組聯合政府失敗，陷入權力真空，國內矛盾令英國難以團結與歐盟談判。"},{"pid":"2d95001475261405e983e7173aa87b4ee73d7e7d","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9gr2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9gr2p8.jpg&h=3f12df6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPicture shows letter triggering Article 50 delivered to @eucopresident.<br />\n<br />\nThe #Brexit countdown begins <br />\n<br />\nbbc.in/2nLlrsf #BrexitDay"},{"pid":"dfcf79bb417c2a21b51e680cc4370b37ed2c71cc","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44678bfc79591326f55b3773d32517251fa95053","tid":178214,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"封信內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ye8nFJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYe8nFJh.jpg&h=04ae51fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37d63ba064305e9fd83c09f423774f3c5f0497c4","tid":178214,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"遊戲：「發動魔法咭，英國脫歐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"}]}